magnate.ui.graphics

Class Tokens

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • magnate.ui.graphics.Tokens
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, java.util.Observer, javax.accessibility.Accessible, Parameters

    public class Tokens
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements Parameters, java.util.Observer
    This class contains part of the tokens of the given player. The attribute 'crowns', defines the type of the tokens to be displayed. The extra wrapper (panel) is needed so that the main panel position dont warp when the images are clicked and text is added below.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Filipe
